/************************/

h1 {
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-weight: 300;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  line-height: 1.5; }

h2 {
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 300;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  line-height: 1.5; }

p {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: #717f92;
  line-height: 3rem;
  margin-bottom: 3rem; }

button {
  border-radius: .5rem;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  border: .1rem solid transparent;
  padding: 1rem 2rem;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  min-width: 17rem;
  transition: .5s; }
  button:focus {
    outline: 0; }

.mirror {

.cta-primary {
  background-color: #2ba6f2;
  color: white;
  margin: 1rem; }
  .cta-primary:hover {
    background-color: black;
    cursor: pointer; }

.cta-secondary {
  background-color: transparent;
  border: .2rem solid #2ba6f2;
  color: #2ba6f2;
  margin: 1rem; }
  .cta-secondary:hover {
    border: .2rem solid black;
    color: black;
    cursor: pointer; }

.learn-more {
  color: #014470;
  cursor: pointer; }

/************************/
/********NAVIGATION******/
/************************/
.topnav {
  height: 4rem;
  background: linear-gradient(0deg, #003050, #034b7a);
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: white; }

.topnav li {
  margin-left: 2rem; }
  .topnav li:first-child {
    margin-left: 0; }

.topnav-login {
  padding: .7rem;
  background-color: #2ba6f2;
  border-radius: .5rem; }

.topnav a {
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none; }

.mainnav {
  height: 6.5rem;
  background: linear-gradient(0deg, white, #f4f4f4);
  box-shadow: 0 0.05rem 0.4rem 0.1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2; }

.logo {
  max-height: 2rem;
  max-width: 20rem; }

.nav-item {
  margin-left: 3rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  border-bottom: .2rem solid #fff; }
  .nav-item:hover {
    border-bottom: .2rem solid #2ba6f2; }

.nav-active {
  border-bottom: .2rem solid #2ba6f2; }

.dropdown-item {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  padding: 2rem; }

.fixed-navigation {
  position: fixed;
  width: 100%;
  z-index: 3; }

/************************/
/********LANDING*********/
/************************/
.landing-section {
  padding: 18rem 0 6rem 0;
  background-color: #f4f7fb;
  border-bottom: .1rem solid #e6e6e6; }

.intro-message {
  background-color: white;
  box-shadow: 0.05rem 0.05rem 1rem 0.1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  border-radius: .5rem; }

.header-image {
  bottom: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: absolute;
  right: 0;
  width: 60%; }

.parallax {
  width: 100%; }

@media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
  .header-image {
    display: none; } }

/************************/
/********SECTION*********/
/************************/
.benefit-section, .cta-section, .blog-section, .blog-section {
  padding: 6rem 0;
  border-bottom: .1rem solid #e6e6e6; }

.benefit-item:nth-child(odd) {
  flex-direction: row-reverse; }

.enter {
  animation: fadein 1s; }

.feature-image-container {
  overflow: hidden; }

.feature-image {
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: .2rem solid #2ba6f2; }

.social-section {
  height: 40rem;
  background: linear-gradient(0deg, #003050, #034b7a);
  color: white; }

.social-image-container {
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  height: 40rem;
  overflow: hidden; }

.social-image {
  width: 100%; }

@media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
  .social-image {
    display: none; }
  .social-quote {
    padding: 4rem !important; } }

.social-quote {
  background: linear-gradient(0deg, #003050, #034b7a); }

.social-quote p {
  color: white !important;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 1.8rem; }

.social-quote p span {
  font-weight: 300;
  font-style: italic; }

.blog-article-site {
  background: linear-gradient(0deg, #003050, #034b7a);
  height: 30rem;
  text-align: center;
  color: white;
  padding: 6rem;
  transition: .5s; }

.blog-article-site:hover {
  border-bottom: 1rem solid #2ba6f2;
  cursor: pointer;
  color: #fff;
  text-decoration: none; }

.blog-article-site h2 {
  margin-bottom: 0; }

.blog-article-site:nth-child(2) {
  border-left: .2rem solid white;
  border-right: .2rem solid white; }

@media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
  .blog-article-site:nth-child(2) {
    border: none;
    border-bottom: .2rem solid white;
    border-top: .2rem solid white; } }

/************************/
/*******MAIN FOOTER******/
/************************/
.main-footer {
  padding: 5rem 0;
  margin-top: 5rem;
  background: linear-gradient(0deg, white, #f4f4f4);
  box-shadow: 0 -0.05rem 0.4rem 0.1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); }

.main-footer ul {
  line-height: 2;
  font-size: 1.8rem; }

.newsletter-signup {
  line-height: 2;
  font-size: 1.8rem; }

.newsletter-signup h2, .newsletter-signup p {
  margin-bottom: 0;
  line-height: normal; }

.newsletter-signup input {
  width: 75%;
  border: .2rem solid black;
  border-radius: .5rem;
  font-weight: 100;
  padding-left: 1rem; }

.submit-newsletter {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  width: 10%;
  background-color: black;
  color: white;
  display: inline-block;
  border-radius: .5rem;
  font-weight: 100;
  height: 4.2rem;
  padding: 0;
  min-width: 4.2rem;
  margin-left: .2rem; }

.social-icons {
  font-size: 3rem; }

.social-icons i {
  margin-left: 1rem; }

.error-message {
  background-color: #fff;
  border: none; }

/************************/
/*******ABOUT US*********/
/************************/
.about-us-section {
  padding: 18rem 0 6rem 0;
  background-color: #f4f7fb;
  border-bottom: .1rem solid #e6e6e6;
  background-image: url("../static/img/about-us-bg.jpg");
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center; }

.about-message {
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  border-radius: .5rem;
  padding: 2rem 4rem !important; }

/************************/
/*****CONTACT US*********/
/************************/
.contact-us-section {
  padding: 18rem 0 6rem 0;
  background-color: #f4f7fb;
  border-bottom: .1rem solid #e6e6e6;
  background-image: url("../static/img/contact-us-bg.jpg");
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center; }

.contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {
  border: .1rem solid #003050;
  border-radius: .5rem;
  padding: .7rem;
  margin-top: .5rem; }

.contact-form .message {
  height: 10rem; }

.contact-form .send {
  margin: 0; }

.contact-form form {
  width: 100%; }

.contact-form .error {
  color: #ff0000; }

.contact-form .empty-field {
  border: .1rem solid #ff0000; }

/************************/
/*********SIGNUP*********/
/************************/
.signup-section {
  padding: 18rem 0 6rem 0;
  background-color: #f4f7fb;
  border-bottom: .1rem solid #e6e6e6; }

  from {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(3rem); }
